In order to Pika you must have CMake >= 2.6 installed. If you do not have CMake installed you can download it from its website http://www.cmake.org.

libpikacurses - requires a curses compatible library.
libpikaRegExp - requires PCRE or Posix regular expressions.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

Inorder to compile pika

1) make your way to the root folder or the project.
2) at the command line type:
   > mkdir build
   > cd build
   > cmake ../../pika
   > make
   > make install

----------------------------------------------------------------------
   CMake command line arguments
   
   -DCURSES_LIBRARIES
   -DCURSES_INCLUDE_DIR

